  "description": "<i>The Spy Trilogy</i> is an espionage-themed text adventure game (with simple graphics). You play as &quot;Bond&quot;, a new member of the Secret Service, and must graduate from the Agent Training School before being given other adventures. The game consists of three linked episodes, each of which must be completed within a fixed time window. <br><br>The game also features a practice mode which is not timed, but which does not give access to the endgame of each episode. The player controls Bond through a simple two-word text interface. \n",
